RQ1: How large is \(|Y_N|\) given |Y_N^s|

Given a problem consisting of a set of subproblems with \(Y_N^s\) given for each subproblem \(s\), we use a filtering algorithm to find \(Y_N\) and afterwards classify the nondominated points into, extreame, supported non-extreame and unsupported.
